29ee208d6000","tid":1115196,"uid":121243,"like":5,"dislike":6,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T11:49:55.000Z","msg":"有冇人睇過呢個channel<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/nPnNQNCoC9M\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FnPnNQNCoC9M&d=7%2FYu9khx8AV6Haip52opSeTimN4xbKJd0qqIWjmG9ok%3D&h=558e12c7\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/nPnNQNCoC9M</a>"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T15:12:27.000Z","msg":"呢個channel<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">好廢</span></span><br />\n淨係識得<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">故弄玄虛 </span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aouEE5Q.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaouEE5Q.png&h=8e3d249a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n啲金字塔嘅建造時間全部錯曬 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n右手面貢開金字塔建造年份明明係公元後十世紀<br />\n<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Koh_Ker#Complex_of_the_double_sanctuary_Prasat_Thom/Prang\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fen.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FKoh_Ker%23Complex_of_the_double_sanctuary_Prasat_Thom%2FPrang&d=7%2FYu9khx8AV6Haip52opSeTimN4xbKJd0qqIWjmG9ok%3D&h=11611a2e\" target=\"_blank\">https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Koh_Ker#Complex_of_the_double_sanctuary_Prasat_Thom/Prang</a><br />\n左手面奇琴伊察金字塔建造年份都唔係公元前，係8到12世紀<br />\n<br />\n佢質疑進化論嗰度都好有問題<br />\n佢除咗曲解解進化論之外 由直立人到智人其實科學界都搵到相多嘅證據<br />\n但佢就特登skip咗 一下子由猿人跳到人<br />\n<br />\n仲有阿特蘭提斯嗰個<br />\n而家學術界普遍認為柏拉圖所講嘢阿特蘭提斯<br />\n其實係依據希臘人對聖托里尼火山爆發一代接一代嘅口述記憶啟發而成<br />\n佢反而講緊都冇乜可能嘅地方出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實迷呢啲嘢嘅人真係鍾意呢啲嘢嘅話<br />\n用下腦，查下資料<br />\n好多都有科學解釋又或者太多矛盾不攻自破<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n神秘學唔係唔好，但係依家21世紀啦，好心做少少科學求證先至講出嚟啦<br />\n好笑嘅係咁多人睇，又咁多人留言真係信<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n當笑料睇下冇問題，睇得多會壞腦"},{"pid":"5d1cab89c488d52107969cf3b31a0b9f9a5a3a68","tid":1115196,"